ments does not involve analyzing internal and external factors.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 35,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that breaking tasks into smaller steps helps in managing complexity.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 36,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that breaking tasks into smaller steps does not help in managing complexity.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 37,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that assigning responsibilities helps in clarifying roles within a team.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 38,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that assigning responsibilities does not help in clarifying roles within a team.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 39,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that setting a timeline helps in coordinating tasks across different departments.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 40,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that setting a timeline does not help in coordinating tasks across different departments.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 41,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that following the plan ensures that tasks are completed in the right order.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 42,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that following the plan does not ensure that tasks are completed in the right order.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 43,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that monitoring progress helps in identifying potential bottlenecks early.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 44,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that monitoring progress does not help in identifying potential bottlenecks early.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 45,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that reviewing and improving the process after completion enhances future planning.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 46,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that reviewing and improving the process after completion does not enhance future planning.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 47,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that planning is a flexible process that allows for adjustments as needed.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 48,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that planning is not a flexible process and does not allow for adjustments.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 49,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that effective planning leads to better resource utilization and efficiency.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 50,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that effective planning does not lead to better resource utilization and efficiency.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    }\n]\n  ',14,13),(47,'2.3-Prescribing Standard Forms for Various Activities','<div>\n    <h1>2.3 Prescribing Standard Forms for Various Activities</h1>\n    \n    <h2>Introduction</h2>\n    <p>In any organization, business, or government office, different activities require the use of specific documents to ensure uniformity, accuracy, and efficiency. These documents, known as standard forms, are pre-designed templates used for common tasks like applications, reports, requests, and data collection.</p>\n    <p>Using standard forms reduces errors, saves time, and ensures that all necessary details are included in a structured format.</p>\n  \n    <h2>What is a Standard Form?</h2>\n    <p>A standard form is a predefined document that follows a fixed format, ensuring that all users provide information in a uniform and organized manner. These forms are commonly used in banking, education, healthcare, business, and government offices.</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>When you open a bank account, you fill out an account opening form.</li>\n      <li>When you apply for a job, you submit a job application form.</li>\n      <li>When you go to a hospital, you fill out a patient registration form.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>These forms help collect necessary details in a structured and easy-to-read manner.</p>\n  \n    <h2>Importance of Standard Forms</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Consistency</strong> – Ensures uniformity in the way information is collected and processed.</li>\n      <li><strong>Efficiency</strong> – Saves time by reducing the need to create new documents for every activity.</li>\n      <li><strong>Accuracy</strong> – Reduces the chance of missing important details.</li>\n      <li><strong>Legal Compliance</strong> – Some industries require forms to meet legal standards.</li>\n      <li><strong>Easy Record-Keeping</strong> – Helps in organizing and retrieving data quickly.</li>\n    </ul>\n  \n    <h2>Examples of Standard Forms in Different Fields</h2>\n  \n    <h3>1. Banking Sector</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Deposit Slip – Used to deposit money into a bank account.</li>\n      <li>Withdrawal Slip – Used to withdraw cash from an account.</li>\n      <li>Loan Application Form – Used to apply for a loan.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Example:</strong> When you want to deposit ₹5,000 into your savings account, you fill out a Deposit Slip, mentioning your account number, name, and amount.</p>\n  \n    <h3>2. Education Sector</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Admission Form – Used for enrolling students in schools or colleges.</li>\n      <li>Examination Form – Used to register students for exams.</li>\n      <li>Library Membership Form – Used for issuing a library card to students.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Example:</strong> If a student wants to take an exam, they must fill out an Examination Form, mentioning their name, roll number, and subject details.</p>\n  \n    <h3>3. Healthcare Sector</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Patient Registration Form – Collects patient details like name, age, medical history.</li>\n      <li>Doctor’s Prescription Form – Used by doctors to prescribe medicines.</li>\n      <li>Medical Test Request Form – Used for requesting laboratory tests.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Example:</strong> When you visit a hospital for the first time, you fill out a Patient Registration Form to provide your personal and medical history.</p>\n  \n    <h3>4. Business and Office Work</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Job Application Form – Used to apply for a job.</li>\n      <li>Leave Application Form – Used by employees to request leave.</li>\n      <li>Expense Reimbursement Form – Used for claiming work-related expenses.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Example:</strong> If an employee wants to take leave, they must submit a Leave Application Form mentioning the reason and dates of leave.</p>\n  \n    <h3>5. Government Services</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Aadhar Card Application Form – Used to apply for an Aadhar card.</li>\n      <li>Driving License Application Form – Used to apply for a driving license.</li>\n      <li>Income Tax Return Form – Used to file income tax.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Example:</strong> If you need a driving license, you must fill out the Driving License Application Form and provide necessary documents.</p>\n  \n    <h2>Key Elements of a Standard Form</h2>\n    <p>Every standard form generally includes:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Title</strong> – Clearly states the purpose of the form (e.g., \"Job Application Form\").</li>\n      <li><strong>Personal Information</strong> – Name, age, contact details.</li>\n      <li><strong>Specific Details</strong> – Information relevant to the form’s purpose (e.g., amount for a deposit slip).</li>\n      <li><strong>Signature</strong> – Space for the applicant\'s signature.</li>\n      <li><strong>Date</strong> – Date of form submission.</li>\n    </ul>\n  \n    <h2>Conclusion</h2>\n    <p>Standard forms are essential for organizing and streamlining activities in various fields. They ensure efficiency, accuracy, and uniformity in information collection. Whether it is banking, healthcare, education, or government services, standard forms play a crucial role in everyday activities.</p>\n    <p>By using pre-designed formats, organizations can save time, reduce errors, and ensure compliance with rules and regulations.</p>\n</div>\n  ','[\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"question\": \"What is a standard form?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"A random document with no structure\",\n        \"A predefined document with a fixed format\",\n        \"A handwritten note\",\n        \"An informal agreement between two parties\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 2,\n      \"question\": \"Which sector commonly uses deposit and withdrawal slips?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Healthcare sector\",\n        \"Education sector\",\n        \"Banking sector\",\n        \"Government services\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 3,\n      \"question\": \"Which of the following is NOT a benefit of using standard forms?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Ensures consistency\",\n        \"Saves time\",\n        \"Increases errors\",\n        \"Helps in record-keeping\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 4,\n      \"question\": \"Why are standard forms used in various fields?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"To ensure accuracy and uniformity\",\n        \"To create confusion\",\n        \"To increase paperwork\",\n        \"To eliminate rules and regulations\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 5,\n      \"question\": \"Which element is commonly included in a standard form?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Personal information\",\n        \"Random images\",\n        \"Blank spaces only\",\n        \"Unstructured text\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 6,\n      \"question\": \"Which of the following is an example of a government service form?\",\n      \"options\": [\n     