d forms help in ________ errors and missing important details.\",\n      \"options\": [\"increasing\", \"reducing\", \"ignoring\", \"encouraging\"],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 4,\n      \"question\": \"A job application form is used when applying for a ________.\",\n      \"options\": [\"loan\", \"passport\", \"job\", \"medical test\"],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 5,\n      \"question\": \"A deposit slip is used in the ________ sector.\",\n      \"options\": [\"healthcare\", \"education\", \"banking\", \"government\"],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 6,\n      \"question\": \"A student needs to fill an ________ form to register for exams.\",\n      \"options\": [\"admission\", \"examination\", \"library\", \"withdrawal\"],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 7,\n      \"question\": \"A patient registration form is used in ________.\",\n      \"options\": [\"schools\", \"hospitals\", \"banks\", \"government offices\"],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 8,\n      \"question\": \"A standard form helps in easy ________ and retrieval of data.\",\n      \"options\": [\"misplacement\", \"destruction\", \"record-keeping\", \"deletion\"],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 9,\n      \"question\": \"A driving license application form is required to obtain a ________.\",\n      \"options\": [\"passport\", \"voter ID\", \"driving license\", \"ration card\"],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 10,\n      \"question\": \"Forms ensure that all necessary details are included in a ________ format.\",\n      \"options\": [\"structured\", \"confusing\", \"incomplete\", \"random\"],\n      \"answer\": 1\n    }\n]\n  ','[\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that standard forms ensure uniformity, accuracy, and efficiency in various activities.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 2,\n      \"question\": \"It is false that standard forms are only used in the healthcare sector.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 3,\n      \"question\": \"A standard form is a pre-designed template used for common tasks.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 4,\n      \"question\": \"Standard forms increase errors and inconsistencies in data collection.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 5,\n      \"question\": \"A bank account opening form is an example of a standard form.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 6,\n      \"question\": \"Standard forms are only used in government offices.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 7,\n      \"question\": \"A job application form helps in applying for a job.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 8,\n      \"question\": \"It is false that using standard forms saves time.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 9,\n      \"question\": \"Deposit slips and withdrawal slips are examples of standard forms in banking.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 10,\n      \"question\": \"A loan application form is required to withdraw money from a bank account.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 11,\n      \"question\": \"Admission forms are used for enrolling students in schools and colleges.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 12,\n      \"question\": \"Library membership forms are used in hospitals.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 13,\n      \"question\": \"An examination form is necessary for registering students for exams.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 14,\n      \"question\": \"Standard forms are not useful for record-keeping.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 15,\n      \"question\": \"A doctor’s prescription form is an example of a standard form in healthcare.\",\n      \"answer\": true