  \"question\": \"It is true that a supervisor in a restaurant does not need to ensure that the dining area is properly arranged.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 38,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that organizing physical resources includes maintaining office equipment.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 39,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that organizing at the supervisory level does not involve managing physical resources like tools and machines.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 40,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that a supervisor must ensure that physical resources are properly maintained.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 41,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that organizing physical resources does not impact the efficiency of workflow.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 42,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that a supervisor is responsible for ensuring that physical resources are efficiently utilized.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 43,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that organizing at the supervisory level involves only ensuring that tasks are allocated.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 44,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that a supervisor must ensure that physical resources are available when needed.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 45,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that organizing physical resources does not reduce wastage of materials.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 46,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that a supervisor in a manufacturing setting does not need to ensure that machines are working properly.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 47,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that organizing at the supervisory level involves ensuring smooth operations in an organization.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 48,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that a supervisor does not need to ensure that infrastructure is maintained.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 49,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that organizing physical resources includes ensuring that workspace is safe.\",\n      \"answer\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 50,\n      \"question\": \"It is true that organizing at the supervisory level does not involve coordinating manpower and materials.\",\n      \"answer\": false\n    }\n]\n  ',14,13),(50,'2.6-Matching Human Needs with Job Needs','<div>\n    <h1>2.6 Matching Human Needs with Job Needs</h1>\n    <p>Every worker has different skills, abilities, and interests. A good supervisor ensures that employees are assigned tasks that match their capabilities while also considering their personal needs.</p>\n    \n    <h2>Key Aspects:</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Job Suitability</strong> – Assigning tasks based on skills and qualifications.</li>\n      <li><strong>Employee Satisfaction</strong> – Ensuring employees feel comfortable and motivated.</li>\n      <li><strong>Work-Life Balance</strong> – Providing fair working hours and proper rest.</li>\n      <li><strong>Training & Development</strong> – Offering learning opportunities to improve skills.</li>\n    </ul>\n    \n    <h2>Example:</h2>\n    <h3>? In a software company:</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>A tech-savvy employee who enjoys coding is assigned programming tasks.</li>\n      <li>A person with good communication skills is given customer support duties.</li>\n    </ul>\n    \n    <h3>? In a hospital:</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>A highly experienced nurse is assigned critical patient care.</li>\n      <li>A junior nurse is given basic duties with proper training.</li>\n    </ul>\n    \n    <p>If an employee is forced to do work they are not skilled at or interested in, productivity decreases, and job satisfaction goes down.</p>\n</div>\n  ','[\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"question\": \"What is the primary goal of matching human needs with job needs?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"To increase workload\",\n        \"To improve employee satisfaction and productivity\",\n        \"To reduce training costs\",\n        \"To decrease employee morale\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 2,\n      \"question\": \"Why is job suitability important in task assignment?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces employee satisfaction\",\n        \"It increases workload\",\n        \"It ensures tasks are assigned based on skills and qualifications\",\n        \"It decreases productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 3,\n      \"question\": \"What happens when employees are assigned tasks that match their skills?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Productivity decreases\",\n        \"Job satisfaction decreases\",\n        \"Productivity and job satisfaction increase\",\n        \"Work-life balance is disrupted\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 4,\n      \"question\": \"What is the role of a supervisor in ensuring employee satisfaction?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"To assign tasks without considering employee interests\",\n        \"To ensure employees feel comfortable and motivated\",\n        \"To reduce working hours\",\n        \"To eliminate training opportunities\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 5,\n      \"question\": \"Why is work-life balance important for employees?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces productivity\",\n        \"It increases stress\",\n        \"It provides fair working hours and proper rest\",\n        \"It decreases job satisfaction\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 6,\n      \"question\": \"What is the benefit of offering training and development opportunities?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces employee skills\",\n        \"It decreases job satisfaction\",\n        \"It improves employee skills and career growth\",\n        \"It increases costs without benefits\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 7,\n      \"question\": \"In a software company, why would a tech-savvy employee be assigned programming tasks?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Because they have poor communication skills\",\n        \"Because they have no interest in coding\",\n        \"Because it matches their skills and interests\",\n        \"Because it is a low-priority task\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 8,\n      \"question\": \"What happens when an employee is forced to do work they are not skilled at or interested in?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Productivity increases\",\n        \"Job satisfaction increases\",\n        \"Productivity decreases and job satisfaction goes down\",\n        \"Work-life balance improves\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 9,\n      \"question\": \"Why is it important to assign critical patient care to a highly experienced nurse?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Because they are new to the job\",\n        \"Because they have limited skills\",\n        \"Because it matches their experience and skills\",\n        \"Because it is a low-priority task\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 10,\n      \"question\": \"What is the benefit of providing basic duties with proper training to a junior nurse?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces their skills\",\n        \"It decreases job satisfaction\",\n        \"It helps them develop skills and confidence\",\n        \"It increases workload without support\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 11,\n      \"question\": \"How does matching human needs with job needs impact employee morale?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It decreases morale\",\n        \"It has no impact on morale\",\n        \"It increases morale by aligning tasks with skills and interests\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 12,\n      \"question\": \"What is the role of a supervisor in ensuring work-life balance?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"To increase working hours\",\n        \"To provide fair working hours and proper rest\",\n        \"To eliminate breaks\",\n        \"To reduce training opportunities\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 13,\n      \"question\": \"Why is it important to consider employee interests when assigning tasks?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces motivation\",\n        \"It has no impact on motivation\",\n        \"It increases motivation and job satisfaction\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 14,\n      \"question\": \"What happens when employees are not provided with opportunities for training and development?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Their skills improve\",\n        \"Their job satisfaction increases\",\n        \"Their skills stagnate and job satisfaction decreases\",\n        \"Their workload decreases\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 15,\n      \"question\": \"How does matching human needs with job needs impact organizational performance?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It decreases performance\",\n        \"It has no impact on performance\",\n        \"It improves performance by increasing productivity and satisfaction\",\n        \"It only affects employee morale\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 16,\n      \"question\": \"What is an example of matching human needs with job needs in a hospital setting?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Assigning critical care to a junior nurse\",\n        \"Assigning basic duties to a highly experienced nurse\",\n        \"Assigning critical care to an experienced nurse and basic duties to a junior nurse with training\",\n        \"Eliminating training opportunities\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 17,\n      \"question\": \"Why is it important to ensure that employees feel comfortable and motivated?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces productivity\",\n        \"It has no impact on productivity\",\n        \"It increases productivity and job satisfaction\",\n        \"It only affects work-life balance\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 18,\n      \"question\": \"What happens when employees are assigned tasks that do not match their skills or interests?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Productivity increases\",\n        \"Job satisfaction increases\",\n        \"Productivity decreases and job satisfaction goes down\",\n        \"Work-life balance improves\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 19,\n      \"question\": \"How does providing fair working hours impact employee well-being?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces well-being\",\n        \"It has no impact on well-being\",\n        \"It improves well-being by reducing stress\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 20,\n      \"question\": \"What is the benefit of offering learning opportunities to employees?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces their skills\",\n        \"It decreases job satisfaction\",\n        \"It improves skills and career growth\",\n        \"It increases costs without benefits\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 21,\n      \"question\": \"Why is it important for a supervisor to consider employee personal needs?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces employee satisfaction\",\n        \"It has no impact on satisfaction\",\n        \"It increases employee satisfaction and motivation\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 22,\n      \"question\": \"What happens when employees are not provided with proper rest?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Productivity increases\",\n        \"Job satisfaction increases\",\n        \"Productivity decreases and job satisfaction goes down\",\n        \"Work-life balance improves\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 23,\n      \"question\": \"How does matching human needs with job needs impact employee retention?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It decreases retention\",\n        \"It has no impact on retention\",\n        \"It increases retention by improving job satisfaction\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 24,\n      \"question\": \"What is the role of training and development in employee growth?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces employee skills\",\n        \"It has no impact on skills\",\n        \"It improves employee skills and career opportunities\",\n        \"It only affects job satisfaction\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 25,\n      \"question\": \"Why is it important to assign tasks based on employee qualifications?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces productivity\",\n        \"It has no impact on productivity\",\n        \"It increases productivity by ensuring tasks are handled competently\",\n        \"It only affects employee morale\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 26,\n      \"question\": \"What happens when a tech-savvy employee is assigned non-technical tasks?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Productivity increases\",\n        \"Job satisfaction increases\",\n        \"Productivity decreases and job satisfaction goes down\",\n        \"Work-life balance improves\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 27,\n      \"question\": \"How does ensuring work-life balance impact employee health?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces health\",\n        \"It has no impact on health\",\n        \"It improves health by reducing stress\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 28,\n      \"question\": \"What is the benefit of providing opportunities for employee growth and development?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces employee motivation\",\n        \"It has no impact on motivation\",\n        \"It increases employee motivation and job satisfaction\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 29,\n      \"question\": \"Why is it important to match employee skills with job requirements?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces efficiency\",\n        \"It has no impact on efficiency\",\n        \"It increases efficiency by ensuring tasks are handled competently\",\n        \"It only affects employee morale\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 30,\n      \"question\": \"What happens when employees are not given opportunities to develop their skills?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Their skills improve\",\n        \"Their job satisfaction increases\",\n        \"Their skills stagnate and job satisfaction decreases\",\n        \"Their workload decreases\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 31,\n      \"question\": \"How does matching human needs with job needs impact organizational culture?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It decreases positive culture\",\n        \"It has no impact on culture\",\n        \"It improves culture by increasing employee satisfaction\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 32,\n      \"question\": \"What is an example of matching human needs with job needs in a software company?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Assigning programming tasks to someone with poor coding skills\",\n        \"Assigning customer support duties to someone with poor communication skills\",\n        \"Assigning programming tasks to a tech-savvy employee and customer support duties to someone with good communication skills\",\n        \"Eliminating training opportunities\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 33,\n      \"question\": \"Why is it important for a supervisor to ensure that employees have opportunities for growth?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces employee motivation\",\n        \"It has no impact on motivation\",\n        \"It increases employee motivation and job satisfaction\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 34,\n      \"question\": \"What happens when employees are not provided with fair working hours?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Productivity increases\",\n        \"Job satisfaction increases\",\n        \"Productivity decreases and job satisfaction goes down\",\n        \"Work-life balance improves\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 35,\n      \"question\": \"How does matching human needs with job needs impact employee engagement?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It decreases engagement\",\n        \"It has no impact on engagement\",\n        \"It increases engagement by aligning tasks with skills and interests\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 36,\n      \"question\": \"What is the role of a supervisor in ensuring employee skills are utilized effectively?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"To assign tasks without considering employee skills\",\n        \"To ensure tasks are assigned based on employee skills and qualifications\",\n        \"To reduce training opportunities\",\n        \"To eliminate breaks\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 37,\n      \"ques