ills?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Their skills improve\",\n        \"Their job satisfaction increases\",\n        \"Their skills stagnate and job satisfaction decreases\",\n        \"Their workload decreases\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 43,\n      \"question\": \"How does matching human needs with job needs impact employee loyalty?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It decreases loyalty\",\n        \"It has no impact on loyalty\",\n        \"It increases loyalty by improving job satisfaction\",\n        \"It only affects productivity\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 44,\n      \"question\": \"What is the role of a supervisor in ensuring that employees are satisfied with their job assignments?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"To assign tasks without considering employee satisfaction\",\n        \"To ensure employees feel comfortable and motivated with their tasks\",\n        \"To reduce training opportunities\",\n        \"To eliminate breaks\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 45,\n      \"question\": \"Why is it important to provide opportunities for employee development?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It reduces employee skills\",\n        \"It has no impact on skills\",\n        \"It improves employee skills and career growth\",\n        \"It only affects job satisfaction\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 46,\n      \"question\": \"What happens when employees are assigned tasks that align with their skills and interests?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Productivity decreases\",\n        \"Job satisfaction decreases\",\n        \"Productivity and job satisfaction increase\",\n        \"Work-life balance is disrupted\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 47,\n      \"question\": \"How does ensuring that employees have opportunities for growth impact organizational success?\",\n      \"options\": [\n   