ass stops the loop, continue skips the iteration\",\n        \"Pass does nothing, continue skips the iteration\",\n        \"Pass skips the iteration, continue stops the loop\",\n        \"Pass restarts the loop, continue does nothing\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 32,\n      \"question\": \"When should you use the break statement in a loop?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"When you want to skip an iteration\",\n        \"When you want to stop the loop immediately\",\n        \"When you want to do nothing\",\n        \"When you want to restart the loop\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 33,\n      \"question\": \"What happens if a loop completes normally without encountering break?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"The else clause does not execute\",\n        \"The else clause executes\",\n        \"The loop skips to the next iteration\",\n        \"The loop restarts\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 34,\n      \"question\": \"Can the else clause be used with any loop control statement?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"Yes, with break and continue\",\n        \"No, only with break\",\n        \"No, only with continue\",\n        \"Yes, but it only executes with pass\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 35,\n      \"question\": \"What is the effect of using pass in a loop?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It stops the loop\",\n        \"It skips the current iteration\",\n        \"It does nothing and continues\",\n        \"It restarts the loop\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 36,\n      \"question\": \"How does the continue statement affect the loop\'s flow?\",\n      \"options\": [\n        \"It stops the loop\",\n        \"It skips the current iteration and continues\",\n        \"It does nothing\",\n        \"It restarts the loop\"\n      ],\n      \"answer\": 2\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 37,\n      \"quest